>\n仲有咩劉細良，陳雲乜水乜水都好唔好聽太多，坐係冷氣房9up紙上談兵係人都識，同佔中三子有咩分別，梁天琦只係精神偶像，佢自己都知坐緊監唔太知情況，聽下就算，唔好咁上心<br />\n<br />\n記住五大訴求，警察只係盾，敵人係林鄭，唔係打警打黑，做返主線啦，主線爆機支線自可清算，唔好一時憤怒比人拉左去打支線<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港"},{"pid":"493ffc7bddd208dca32b65095c2304fa0fe6ed0b","tid":1381323,"uid":70443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:27:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"16fa62d21fdbfd729e4cbeadd15a449fbc798e7c","tid":1381323,"uid":64744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得經濟損失真係有效過遊行，可能呢個方法難度細過罷工罷課"},{"pid":"23b9ef33cc3254ccecd90bba63c552c437ab4a45","tid":1381323,"uid":194609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16fa62d21fdbfd729e4cbeadd15a449fbc798e7c","tid":1381323,"uid":64744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得經濟損失真係有效過遊行，可能呢個方法難度細過罷工罷課"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:07:04.000Z","msg":"大家一齊企係銅鑼灣唔郁幾日"},{"pid":"fe3e75a84971a58ecea817161b489249d4d0378b","tid":1381323,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8b9381aa540289fb720ec0792c3dc295eb957f","tid":1381323,"uid":263161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d81a6d724cb80398e3555108db90dbae97204ae","tid":1381323,"uid":42942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"不如去高鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25aee629e8d5afea71f18743d2f61d8fd95040f","tid":1381323,"uid":165200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:25:21.000Z","msg":"好似有得諗，人數唔使多，閙市（例：元朗）的話，可能3,000人已經夠，街頭行去街尾，過馬路，反方向行，去返街頭，再過馬路，loop，中間可以過下馬路，即使跟足交通燈過，人多一樣可以影響馬路流量 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cd17724b75fec286b5891655acce9911229379","tid":1381323,"uid":20262,"like":0,"disl